;ELECTRON DENSITY FOR RESIDUE MET A 1 AND MET B 1 IS PRESENT
BUT MODELLING WITH ACCEPTABLE GEOMETRY WAS NOT POSSIBLE.

A CHAIN OF 5 VERY HIGH ELECTRON DENSITY SPHERES ADJACENT
AND ORTHOGONAL TO THE SIDE-CHAIN OF ASP A 2 AND ASP B 2
WAS MODELLED AS ZN-HOH-ZN-HOH-ZN, BUT THE RESOLUTION IS
NOT HIGH ENOUGH FOR UNAMBIGUOUS CHARACTERISATION.
